parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the brake switch can cause the vehicle to not start, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the BCI Malfunction warning light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system drain or short can cause the battery to drain, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The battery drains quickly
the vehicle will not start
the instrument panel lights are dim or out
the vehicle's electrical systems malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the instrument panel lights can make it difficult to see important information, such as speed, leading to safety risks.
symptoms: The instrument panel lights are dim or out
making it difficult to see important information.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: BCI malfunction can cause the vehicle to not start, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The BCI Malfunction warning light comes on
the vehicle will not start
the vehicle's electrical systems malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the airbag system can lead to safety risks in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on
the airbag system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the starter switch can cause the vehicle to not start, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the starter switch malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunction of the navigation system can cause inconvenience and distraction while driving.
symptoms: The navigation system goes blank or flickers
the navigation system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or fail to accelerate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission shifts improperly
hesitates
or fails to engage
causing the vehicle to lose power
stall
or fail to accelerate. The tachometer may flutter or hesitate
and the vehicle may shudder or vibrate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or fail to accelerate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
sticks to the floor
or does not return to its normal position. The vehicle may be unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or fail to accelerate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine may stall
lose power
or fail to accelerate. Cylinder 7 on the engine may have significant scouring
leading to engine failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal switch can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal switch fails to recognize when the brake pedal is applied
causing the vehicle to lose braking ability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag control module can cause the airbag warning light to flash, indicating a potential malfunction of the airbag system, which can lead to failure to deploy in the event of an accident, putting the driver and passengers at risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light flashes
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident
the airbag system malfunctions without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbag sensors can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to failure to deploy in the event of an accident, putting the driver and passengers at risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light flashes
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident
the airbag system malfunctions without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical issues in the airbag system can cause the airbag warning light to flash, indicating a potential malfunction of the airbag system, which can lead to failure to deploy in the event of an accident, putting the driver and passengers at risk of injury or death.
